Why Choose Just Energy
Just Energy serves more than 1.8 million customers across North America. In more than 17 years, Just Energy has established itself as one of the top natural gas and electricity providers in the U.S. and Canada.
More Information


Green Energy Product Options
Just Energy is committed to offering green energy options to residential and commercial customers alike. Support the environment by adding a JustGreen package to your natural gas or electric supply.
More Information


Learning Center
Do you know why it's important to compare electricity rates? Looking for more information on what factors make up the current natural gas price? Find what you're looking for in our Learning Center.
More Information




Work With Us
At Just Energy, we know the success of our people leads to success for our business. Learn more about joining our winning team today!
Visit our career center


Investor Relations
Find quarterly reports, historical profit data, information on our board members and more in our Investor Relations hub.
Learn more about investor relations


Just Energy Foundation
The Just Energy Foundation was established by Just Energy Group Inc. in 2013 as a way to give back to the communities we serve. The Foundation supports local charitable organizations that work to improve the livelihood and well-being of communities in need.
