About Us














Just Energy is a leading provider of natural gas, electricity and green energy. We were established in 1997 and as a publicly traded company (NYSE:JE and TSX:JE), serve more than 2 million customers across North America. Along with electricity and natural gas supply, we offer green energy product options and energy efficient programs that let customers support a cleaner environment.
Our Vision and Pillars
Just Energy stands by its vision to be the gold standard in retail energy delivering stability, value and innovation in every customer, shareholder, employee and community relationship. Our vision serves as the framework for every aspect of our business.




Value
Striving to deliver the highest satisfaction and greatest benefit to every customer shareholder, employee and community partner.


Stability
Ensuring we consistently deliver dependable, predictable products and service, reliable investor return and a strong commitment to the community.


Innovation
Challenging ourselves daily to explore forward-thinking solutions and progressive options to deliver gold standard products and services.




Our Markets
Just Energy currently serves 20 markets across North America, including 14 states and 6 provinces.
More Information


Just Energy Group
Our companies include Amigo Energy, Commerce Energy, Hudson Energy, Tara Energy, Green Star Energy and TerraPass through which Just Energy operates under in certain markets.
More Information


Just Energy Foundation
We are committed to enhancing the livelihood of the communities in which we live, work and play.
More Information




Investor Relations
Get access to investor information, including annual and quarterly reports, financial highlights and historical stock performance.
More Information


Leadership Team
Our leaders have helped make Just Energy one of the leading retail energy providers in North America. Meet the faces behind our exceptional leadership team.
More Information


Career Center
Just Energy is proud to be recognized as one of the Achievers 50 Most Engaged Workplaces. Our Career Center provides information on advancing your career and personal development with Just Energy.
More Information




TerraPass
Unique, sustainable solutions to help energy consumers reduce the environmental footprint of their home, lifestyle or business.
More Information


In the News
Our news section features articles, press releases and announcements to keep you up to date on Just Energy. Also find media contacts here.
More Information


Contact Us
Want to learn more about Just Energy? Contact us and we can help you.
More Information

















