Choose Just Energy’s Electric and Natural Gas Supply Rates for your Home
There's a reason more than 2 million people have chosen Just Energy's electric and natural gas supply supply rates. The next time you compare energy providers, take a close look at what Just Energy has to offer. From secured supply rates to green energy options, Just Energy has distinguished itself among energy providers in North America. Enter your ZIP code now to get residential energy prices from Just Energy!





Experienced
Just Energy has been offering residential customers electric and natural gas rates since 1997. Today, Just Energy and its family of companies that includes Commerce Energy, Tara Energy, Amigo Energy, Green Star, TerraPass, and JE Solar create one of the largest retail energy suppliers in North America.


Peace of Mind
When it comes to energy prices, it's easy to feel overwhelmed. The security offered by Just Energy's secured supply rates and other types of residential energy prices makes it easy to be confident in your choice.





