Convenient Billing Options
While most customers pay their energy bill through their utility, some customers pay Just Energy directly. For those customers, Just Energy offers several billing options to make life easier, such as a mobile app and Auto Pay.

			



Environmental Leadership
Just Energy supports green energy projects across North America. With green energy product options from Just Energy, it's easy to make the world a better place.


Competitive Pricing
Just Energy creates energy plans for all sorts of customers. Whether you're looking to compare electricity supply rates or your current natural gas price, start by seeing what Just Energy has to offer.




Seamless Service
When you choose a plan from Just Energy, you won't experience any service interruptions. Your utility will continue to ensure reliable service and respond to emergencies.






SmartStat
The newest product offering from Just Energy, SmartStat brings home energy use into the 21st century. This learning thermostat, with it's innovative features and quality design, represents the commitment Just Energy makes to its customers and the environment.
